00:46:28.780 --> 00:46:33.160
as something to be
of very high value.

00:46:33.160 --> 00:46:36.680
And obviously that's a very
different view of the self,

00:46:36.680 --> 00:46:39.380
sacrificing the self
for the greater good.

00:46:39.380 --> 00:46:43.860
To bring this back
to China, I think

00:46:43.860 --> 00:46:47.590
we also tend to think of
