00:51:09.760 --> 00:51:12.790
is you begin realizing that
not just Chinese ideas,

00:51:12.790 --> 00:51:16.350
actually if you look at
so-called traditional practices

00:51:16.350 --> 00:51:19.800
in general, a lot of the
