that's precisely the point.

00:51:35.120 --> 00:51:38.830
The whole point of these rituals
is yes, you enter a space

00:51:38.830 --> 00:51:42.010
and you are no longer the
person that you were before.

00:51:42.010 --> 00:51:44.880
You are acting as if
you're a different person

00:51:44.880 --> 00:51:46.190
in a different world.

00:51:46.190 --> 00:51:48.810
And the goal of that is
to change for the better.

00:51:48.810 --> 00:51:51.710
